# Active task backlog (T0068 P2): per-session operational state the loop auto-
# creates/edits, NOT source — without this the loop's auto-add re-tracks active
# task files and leaks them into source commits (the d06155b chore only `git rm
# --cached`'d the symptom). The completed-task record under tasks/archive/ and
# tasks/README.md stay tracked (this anchored pattern matches only direct
# children of tasks/, not tasks/archive/).
/tasks/T*.md
